snippet.title: Just Dance 2016 Official Song List - Part 2 [US]
snippet.description:
New song announcements! Coming to Just Dance 2016 this October:

• Fancy - Iggy Azalea Ft. Charli XCX
• Lights - Ellie Goulding
• Fun - Pitbull Ft. Chris Brown
• Stuck On A Feeling - Prince Royce
• Rabiosa - Shakira Ft. El Cata
• I'm An Albatraoz - AronChupa
• Circus - Britney Spears

AND MANY MORE! 

Introducing a brand new way to play! All you need is your smartphone and the free Just Dance Controller App to play Just Dance 2016 on WiiU, XboxOne, or PS4. No extra accessories or camera needed.  

Try Just Dance 2016 for free this summer! Visit justdancegame.com/app for details. 

Just Dance 2016 will be available on October 20th, 2015 on Wii U, Wii, PS4, PS3, Xbox One and Xbox 360

Visit our Website: http://www.JustDanceGame.com 
Join us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/JustDanceGame
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/JustDanceGame
Follow us on Instagram: https://instagram.com/justdancegame_us 
Add us on Snapchat: Username: JustDance
